alerts.description:

Height range: > 1000 m; Max. gusts: 85-95 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 110 km/h

There is a risk of gale-force gusts (Level 2 of 4).

Max. gusts: 50-60 km/h; Wind direction: south-west; Increased gusts: in exposed locations ~ 65 km/h

Precipitation amounts: ~ 25 l/m²/6h
